name: Prototype 6
description:
Flux apparatus with assymetry

Man portable version of larger flux device discovered earlier (Ref: NDN-145)

Operational, but testing is limited by minimal fuel reserves.  Unclear if ionizing radiation (well regulated) is purpose, or side effect of unknown function. Pronounced voltage gap on opposite sides of protuberance.

Bench tests TBD.

Oscilloscope Art - XY oscilloscope trace of custom designed audio sample.  Background audio (warning: noisy!) is the custom audio signal used to create the line drawings.  Modern data fed into obsolete tech.  30 second loop.  60fps.
